avatar.msg: Responds with the avatar of the user, if no user is written, your avatar

comics.msg: Get a random comic from a bunch of different artists

drama.msg: Responds with a drama image, if no number is written, a random one

emoji.msg: Responds with an emoji copypasta, if no number is written, a random one

gif.msg:
Gets a gif from Giphy or Popkey matching the given tags.
Use `!giphy` or `!popkey` to search the specific sites

help_memelist.msg: List of meme names for the **`!meme`** command

join.msg: Joins the server the bot is invited to

meme.msg: Creates a meme with the given meme name and text

paste.msg: Creates a paste on Pastebin.com and returns the url

quote.msg: Responds with a quote, if no number is written, a random one

roll.msg: Rolls the dice a number of times with a number of sides

serverlist.msg: Lists all the servers the bot is connected to

servers.msg: Lists how many servers, channels and users the bot is connected to

uptime.msg: Shows how long the bot has been online

urban.msg: Returns the summary of the first matching search result from Urban Dictionary

userinfo.msg: Gives information about the user, if no user is written, yourself

version.msg: Get information on the latest version of Gravebot

videocall.msg: Start a one click video call or screenshare directly on Appear.in. Mention users to make it private.

wiki.msg: Returns the summary of the first matching search result from Wikipedia

wolfram.msg: Query Wolfram Alpha for almost anything

youtube.msg: Gets a video from Youtube matching the given tags
